| Table Name            | Column Name             | Data Type (SQL Server) | Max Length (VARCHAR) | Is Nullable | Description     |
|-----------------------|-------------------------|-------------------------|----------------------|-------------|------------------|
| User                  | UserID                  | INT                     |                      | NO          | Unique identifier for user |
|                       | Username                | VARCHAR                 | 50                   | NO          | The user's name   |
|                       | Password                | VARCHAR                 | 255                  | NO          | Hashed password    |
|                       | Email                   | VARCHAR                 | 100                  | NO          | User email address |
| TailorProfile         | ProfileID               | INT                     |                      | NO          | Unique identifier for tailor profile |
|                       | UserID                  | INT                     |                      | NO          | Reference to user  |
|                       | TailorDescription       | VARCHAR                 | 500                  | YES         | Description of tailor  |
| RoomChat              | ChatRoomID              | INT                     |                      | NO          | Unique identifier for chat room |
|                       | TailorProfileID         | INT                     |                      | NO          | Reference to tailor profile |
|                       | UserID                  | INT                     |                      | NO          | Reference to user  |
| Chat                  | ChatID                  | INT                     |                      | NO          | Unique identifier for chat |
|                       | ChatRoomID              | INT                     |                      | NO          | Reference to chat room |
|                       | Message                 | TEXT                    |                      | YES         | The message content |
|                       | SenderID                | INT                     |                      | NO          | ID of sender     |
| RatingReview          | ReviewID                | INT                     |                      | NO          | Unique identifier for review |
|                       | UserID                  | INT                     |                      | NO          | ID of the user who submitted review |
|                       | TailorProfileID         | INT                     |                      | NO          | ID of the reviewed tailor |
|                       | Rating                  | INT                     |                      | NO          | Rating given by user |
|                       | Comment                 | TEXT                    |                      | YES         | Review comment     |
| Province              | ProvinceID              | INT                     |                      | NO          | Unique identifier for province |
|                       | ProvinceName            | VARCHAR                 | 100                  | NO          | Name of the province |
| Regency               | RegencyID               | INT                     |                      | NO          | Unique identifier for regency |
|                       | ProvinceID              | INT                     |                      | NO          | Reference to province  |
|                       | RegencyName             | VARCHAR                 | 100                  | NO          | Name of the regency  |
| District              | DistrictID              | INT                     |                      | NO          | Unique identifier for district |
|                       | RegencyID               | INT                     |                      | NO          | Reference to regency |
|                       | DistrictName            | VARCHAR                 | 100                  | NO          | Name of the district |
| Village               | VillageID               | INT                     |                      | NO          | Unique identifier for village |
|                       | DistrictID              | INT                     |                      | NO          | Reference to district |
|                       | VillageName             | VARCHAR                 | 100                  | NO          | Name of the village  |
| Order                 | OrderID                 | INT                     |                      | NO          | Unique identifier for order |
|                       | UserID                  | INT                     |                      | NO          | Reference to user  |
|                       | OrderDate               | DATETIME                |                      | NO          | Date of the order  |
|                       | TotalAmount             | DECIMAL(18, 2)         |                      | NO          | Total price of order |
| OrderShipping         | ShippingID              | INT                     |                      | NO          | Unique identifier for shipping |
|                       | OrderID                 | INT                     |                      | NO          | Reference to order  |
|                       | ShippingAddress         | VARCHAR                 | 255                  | NO          | Address for shipping |
|                       | ShippingDate            | DATETIME                |                      | NO          | When the order was shipped |
| OrderCancellation     | CancellationID          | INT                     |                      | NO          | Unique identifier for cancellation |
|                       | OrderID                 | INT                     |                      | NO          | Reference to order  |
|                       | CancellationReason       | TEXT                    |                      | YES         | Reason for cancellation |
| OrderItem            | ItemID                 | INT                     |                      | NO          | Unique identifier for order item |
|                       | OrderID                 | INT                     |                      | NO          | Reference to order  |
|                       | ProductID               | INT                     |                      | NO          | ID of the product  |
|                       | Quantity                | INT                     |                      | NO          | Quantity ordered   |
| Article               | ArticleID               | INT                     |                      | NO          | Unique identifier for article |
|                       | Title                   | VARCHAR                 | 255                  | NO          | Title of the article |
|                       | Content                 | TEXT                    |                      | YES         | The content of the article |
| Course                | CourseID                | INT                     |                      | NO          | Unique identifier for course |
|                       | Title                   | VARCHAR                 | 255                  | NO          | Title of the course |
|                       | Description             | TEXT                    |                      | YES         | Description of the course  |
| Stuff                 | StuffID                 | INT                     |                      | NO          | Unique identifier for stuff |
|                       | Name                    | VARCHAR                 | 255                  | NO          | Name of the stuff |
|                       | Details                 | TEXT                    |                      | YES         | Details about the stuff |